Source: SBD > CM > DAT > CDR > EAC > Soundforge > CD-Wave > 
TLH v.1.0.0.72 (for SBE-OK, FLAC compression & checksums) > 
FLAC, October 2006. 

Notes: This was the last JGB show with Bill Kreutzmann, 
Jimmy Warren, Essra Mowhawk, and Liz Stires. Some of the 
songs start abruptly due to tape pauses. The very end of 
Run for the Roses is clipped. Soundforge was used to make 
fades, adjust levels, and for some small edits. With big 
thanks to Jon P for transferring his DAT to CDR. EAC thru 
FLAC by Andrew F.                          ****ENJOY****
